        </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-7">
            <h5>Step 3: Measure Weights</h5>
            <p>
                Measure the following weights (in grams):
                <ul class="text-start">
                    <li><strong>Whole weight</strong>: The total weight of the entire abalone, including the shell and meat.</li>
                    <li><strong>Shucked weight</strong>: The weight of the abalone meat, excluding the shell.</li>
                    <li><strong>Viscera weight</strong>: The weight of the internal organs (gut weight) after bleeding.</li>
                    <li><strong>Shell weight</strong>: The weight of the shell, measured after it has been dried.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4: Submit Your Data -->
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h5>Step 4: Submit Your Data</h5>
            <p>
                Enter the measurements into the submission form, and you'll instantly get the estimated age of your abalone.
                <br><br>
                <strong>Optional:</strong> If you'd like to share your abalone with others, you can upload a photo, and it will be featured in the gallery for everyone to see!
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 text-center">
            <img src="./images/guide-step3.png" alt="Guide Step 3" class="img-fluid rounded mb-3">
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Call-to-Action -->
    <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <h3>Ready to Estimate?</h3>
        <a href="/Upload" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-3">Submit Your Data Now</a>
    </div>
</div>
